    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="I want to put my novel&#39;s title on the cover" class="article-title">
          I want to put my novel&#39;s title on the cover
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>You can set the title to display on the cover through the cover template settings reachable from the novel posting page.<br>You cannot upload images from the app.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>If you want to upload your own cover image</h3>
<p>Please take a look at the process below.<br><a href="https://www.pixiv.help/hc/ja/articles/235584208-%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AC%E3%81%AE%E8%A1%A8%E7%B4%99%E3%82%92%E8%87%AA%E4%BD%9C%E3%81%AE%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A7%E3%81%8D%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99%E3%81%8B-" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Is the novel cover an illustration you made yourself?</a></p>
<p><br><a href="#h_01EECHQ4Y5MJSJJ08TJR91P08V" target="_self" rel="undefined">▶︎On desktop</a><br><a href="#h_01EECHQHEM5214P02N1DF1Z5DW" target="_self" rel="undefined">▶︎On mobile</a><br><a href="#h_01EKF3ZV48VV5H3Y82C3MH5G8K" target="_self">▶︎App version</a></p>
<h3 id="h_01EECHQ4Y5MJSJJ08TJR91P08V">On desktop</h3>
<p>Please select the cover template you want from the list.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672386/mceclip0.png" alt="mceclip0.png" width="735" height="422"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you click "See all", then all of the cover templates will display.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672726/mceclip5.png" alt="mceclip5.png"></p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/8938421234457/___________182_.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/8938421234457/___________182_.png" alt="___________182_.png"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The title displayed on the image can be edited by clicking "Cover settings".<br>The button is displayed to the right of "Cover preview".<br><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672426/mceclip2.png" alt="mceclip2.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can enable and disable the display of the title, the title text displayed, the font, and the color via the "Cover settings" menu.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672466/mceclip3.png" alt="mceclip3.png"></p>
<h4>&nbsp;</h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01EECHQHEM5214P02N1DF1Z5DW">On mobile</h3>
<p>Please select the cover template you want from the list.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002652123/mceclip6.png" alt="mceclip6.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you click "See all", then all of the cover templates will display.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002652163/mceclip7.png" alt="mceclip7.png"></p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/8938494368665/___________183_.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/8938494368665/___________183_.png" alt="___________183_.png" width="469" height="615"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The title displayed on the image can be edited by clicking "Cover settings".<br>The button is displayed to the right of "Cover preview".<br><br><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002674466/mceclip9.png" alt="mceclip9.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can enable and disable the display of the title, the title text displayed, the font, and the color via the "Cover settings" menu.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002652283/mceclip10.png" alt="mceclip10.png"></p>
<h4>&nbsp;</h4>
<h3 id="h_01EKF3ZV48VV5H3Y82C3MH5G8K">▶︎App version</h3>
<p>You can not edit the cover title from the app. Additionally, you can not insert a title on desktop or mobile for covers set from the app.</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

